              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2513987-janice?shelf=z-read-in-2019">z-read-in-2019</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer349598550" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16631321588960628116">This is a different approach to the legend of King Arthur. I enjoyed it, but will likely not continue with the series.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


