        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1321208266" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1321208266&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F146690.Hawk_of_May">flag</a>





