    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2762369096" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2762369096" />
    <a title="Lori" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/45385863-lori"><img alt="Lori" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1437857317p2/45385863.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2762369096?book_show_action=true">Mar 24, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lori" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lori" href="/user/show/45385863-lori">Lori</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781402240706" href="/book/show/8237755-hawk-of-may">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2762369096" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10001756113374260815">Another perspective on the Arthurian tales. I enjoyed this discovery (bookshelf at a Friends of the Library used book sale) and am glad to find out it is a trilogy. The language was challenging as she used a mingling of ancient names for characters and places but there was enough intrigue to carry the reader past those difficulties. Not a great read but a good enough one to put the next book on my TBR list.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

